description: Kevin Keller is the new kid in Riverdale and the gang has made him feel right at home. When Wit Masters, a trivia game show for rival high schools comes around, Dilton and the crew want Kevin to represent them for the win. Too bad Kevin has a fear of public speaking. Will he pull it off and get Riverdale the winning championship for the third year in a row or will he choke in front of the big lights?
name: Let's Get It Started

description: The acclaimed series comes to print, spinning the pure-fun yarn of heroine Bonnie Lass setting out to build her reputation as a pirate to be envied and feared. Bent on overshadowing her father, the infamous Cutlass, Bonnie's after the one treasure he did not claim - the Eye of the Leviathan. Humor, beauty, misdirection, mash-ups and a leading lady to fall for sets sail on the open seas.
name: The Legend, Part One

description: Spirited modern-day she-pirate, Bonnie Lass, has her hands on the mysterious map that even her legendary pirate father could not decipher. With more pluck than plan, her crew sets sail to find some treasure, kick some tail, raise some eyebrows, and deal with some daddy issues.
name: The Legend, Part Two

description: This issue consists of a hand painted figurine and a magazine on the issues featured character.
name: Hourman (Rick Tyler)
